Package: SpeTestNP
Type: Package
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2022-09-05
Imports:
  np
Suggests: 
  pracma, foreach
Title: Nonparametric Testing for Linear Models
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hippolyte", "Boucher", email = "Hippolyte.Boucher@outlook.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Pascal", "Lavergne", email = "lavergnetse@gmail.com", role = "cre"))
Maintainer: 
  Pascal Lavergne <lavergnetse@gmail.com>
Description: 
    The package performs nonparametric test of linearity. Five heteroskedasticity-robust tests are
    available: Bierens (1982), Zheng (1996), Escanciano (2006), Lavergne and Patilea (2008),
    and Lavergne and Patilea (2012). Specific bandwidth and kernel methods can be chosen along
    with many other options.
